            by infusing Nissan’s Japanese heritage and aesthetics. <br>
                 Nissan it will be offer a autonomous technologies. <br><br>
           
             2). X-motion represents the endless possibilities of how people can relate to the design.  <br>
             The MG Xmotion car will feature an electric powertrain, interconnection, intelligence and information sharing.  <br><br>
              
             3). The power of a inteligent grip. Toyota Rav4 Hybrid`s electronic provides all-weather capability and confident on-road driving dynamics. <br>
             This car uses a dedicated electric drive motor to automatically supply power to the rear wheels for instant improvement in traction.  <br><br>
              
             4). The BMW I8 is defined by its driving experience though.  <br>
                 The combination of a small petrol engine and electric motor is a technological tour de force and means it’s easy to drive.  <br>
                 With this car it`s easy to drive fast also.  <br><br>
              
             5). Nothing compares to a classic technology.  <br>
                 The 1996 Toyota Supra had a 3.0-liter, six-cylinder engine with 220 horsepower.  <br>
